observations.recommendation:
We recommended that Management:
Prepare and submit Report on Physical Count of PPE for the current year 2019 to determine the actual physical count and condition of PPE at a given date including those unrecorded newly purchased and those which could not be accounted for; 

 Physical inventory taking of properties by type shall be conducted annually and Direct the Property Custodian to identify the unserviceable properties already subjected for disposal and prepare the Inventory and Inspection Report of Unserviceable Property.

We recommended that Management :

Intensify the immediate collections of the account dues from the officers and employees concerned; 	

Refrain or stop this malpractice to use government fund for the payment of personal loan amortization of the officers and employees;

Non-settlement and/or complete disregard to settle their accounts shall constitute a ground for the withholding of their salaries, and the auditor is compelled to issue Demand Letter and/or make a narrative report to apply the sanctions under the provisions of Art. 217 and 220 of the Revised Penal Code.

